window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Meet Ramona. She lives on Klickitat Street with her mother, father, and big sister, Beezus. She’s not afraid of anything and is always up to something. And that’s just the beginning…. </p> <p>In this audio collection, join Ramona, one of Beverly Cleary’s most beloved characters, on all her wacky adventures! This collection includes:</p> <p><i>Beezus and Ramona</i><br><i>Ramona the Pest</i><br><i>Ramona the Brave</i><br><i>Ramona and Her Father</i><br><i>Ramona and Her Mother </i><br><i>Ramona Quimby, Age 8 </i><br><i>Ramona Forever</i><br><i>Ramona's World</i></p>"; 
